The course offers an opportunity to understand and analyse human rights and professional ethics in youth work and to develop value-based practices.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The student values the rights and professional ethics of young people and follows them in organizing youth work.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student:  - interprets the key concepts of ethics and values;  - understands the professional ethics of youth work and its practical application;  - analyses, on the basis of value-based youth work, opportunities for support to participate in youth activities;  - values human rights, including the rights of young people, and their meaning in youth work.
